OL,3,CNew Babies on Board badge for women
OL,4,Cpregnant with twins or more
OL,6,FA new badge has been created to help
OL,7,Fwomen pregnant with multiple babies
OL,8,Fget a seat on public transport.
OL,10,FTransport for London (TfL) launched
OL,11,Fthe Babies on Board badge to mark the
OL,12,F20th anniversary of the introduction
OL,13,Fof the Baby on Board design.
OL,15,FPassengers sitting on busy buses and
OL,16,Ftrains are asked to give up their seat
OL,17,Fwhen they see a badge wearer having to
OL,18,Fstand.
OL,20,FMore than 80,000 Baby on Board badges
OL,21,Fare given out every year.
