OL,3,CNew Babies on Board badge for women
OL,4,Cpregnant with twins or more
OL,6,FThey were launched in March 2006
OL,7,Ffolowing research that found pregnant
OL,8,Fwomen on the Tube were made to stand
OL,9,Ffor an average of five stops before
OL,10,Fbeing offered a seat and 35% were
OL,11,Fnever offered a seat.
OL,13,FThe free badges can be ordered through
OL,14,FTfL's website or collected at the
OL,15,Ftransport body's visitor centres at
OL,16,Fmajor stations.
OL,18,FTfL also has a partnership with
OL,19,Fretailer John Lewis and fashion brand
OL,20,FUniqlo.
