CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1774447875
OL,3,CNew Babies on Board badge for women
OL,4,Cpregnant with twins or more
OL,6,FDeputy Mayor for transport Seb Dance
OL,7,Fsaid asking Londoners to be "mindful
OL,8,Fof those who may need a seat more than
OL,9,Fthem" is key to making public
OL,10,Ftransport "as accessible as possible".
OL,12,FTfL customer director Emma Strain said
OL,13,Fthe new badge design will ensure
OL,14,F"every expectant parent feels
OL,15,Fsupported and seen".
OL,17,FShauna Leven, chief executive of
OL,18,Fcharity Twins Trust, said: "We're
OL,19,Fthrilled to hear that parents
OL,20,Fexpecting multiples can now get a
OL,21,FBabies on Board badge.
