OL,3,CNew Babies on Board badge for women
OL,4,Cpregnant with twins or more
OL,6,F"For expectants pregnant with twins,
OL,7,Ftriplets or more, life can be more
OL,8,Fchallenging as they might face a high-
OL,9,Frisk pregnancy, extreme tiredness and
OL,10,Fmorning sickness."
